Package co.edu.unbosque.electroshop_api.model

Class Customer

java.lang.Object
co.edu.unbosque.electroshop_api.model.Customer
@Entity public class Customer extends Object
Represents a customer in the system.

This class is an entity representing a client with various personal details. Includes attributes such as the customer's ID, name, last name, gender, phone number, address, and email. It also maintains a one-to-many relationship with the Order entity.
